1765 void StatementBinder::Visit(ConditionalCompilationStatementNode& conditionalCompilationStatementNode)
1766 {
1767     conditionalCompilationStatementNode.IfPart()->Accept(*this);
1768     bool defined = conditionalCompilationStack.top();
1769     conditionalCompilationStack.pop();
1770     if (defined)
1771     {
1772         int n = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.IfPart()->Statements().Count();
1773         if (n > 0)
1774         {
1775             for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
1776             {
1777                 StatementNode* statement = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.IfPart()->Statements()[i];
1778                 statement->Accept(*this);
1779             }
1780         }
1781         else
1782         {
1783             AddStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, conditionalCompilationStatementNode.GetSpan()));
1784         }
1785     }
1786     else
1787     {
1788         bool executed = false;
1789         int n = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.ElifParts().Count();
1790         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
1791         {
1792             ConditionalCompilationPartNode* elifPart = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.ElifParts()[i];
1793             elifPart->Accept(*this);
1794             bool defined = conditionalCompilationStack.top();
1795             conditionalCompilationStack.pop();
1796             if (defined)
1797             {
1798                 int n = elifPart->Statements().Count();
1799                 if (n > 0)
1800                 {
1801                     for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
1802                     {
1803                         StatementNode* statement = elifPart->Statements()[i];
1804                         statement->Accept(*this);
1805                     }
1806                 }
1807                 else
1808                 {
1809                     AddStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, conditionalCompilationStatementNode.GetSpan()));
1810                 }
1811                 executed = true;
1812                 break;
1813             }
1814         }
1815         if (!executed)
1816         {
1817             ConditionalCompilationPartNode* elsePart = conditionalCompilationStatementNode.ElsePart();
1818             if (elsePart)
1819             {
1820                 int n = elsePart->Statements().Count();
1821                 if (n > 0)
1822                 {
1823                     for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
1824                     {
1825                         StatementNode* statement = elsePart->Statements()[i];
1826                         statement->Accept(*this);
1827                     }
1828                 }
1829                 else
1830                 {
1831                     AddStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, conditionalCompilationStatementNode.GetSpan()));
1832                 }
1833             }
1834             else
1835             {
1836                 AddStatement(new BoundEmptyStatement(module, conditionalCompilationStatementNode.GetSpan()));
1837             }
1838         }
1839     }
1840 }

1868 void StatementBinder::AddReleaseExceptionStatement(const Span& span)
1869 {
1870     if (insideCatch && !compilingReleaseExceptionStatement)
1871     {
1872         compilingReleaseExceptionStatement = true;
1873         InvokeNode * invokeNode(new InvokeNode(span, new DotNode(span, new IdentifierNode(span, U"@exPtr"), new IdentifierNode(span, U"Release"))));
1874         ExpressionStatementNode releaseExceptionStatement(span, invokeNode);
1875         CompileStatement(&releaseExceptionStatement, true);
1876         compilingReleaseExceptionStatement = false;
1877     }

1880 void StatementBinder::AddStatement(BoundStatement* boundStatement)
1881 {
1882     if (postfix)
1883     {
1884         boundStatement->SetPostfix();
1885     }
1886     if (statement)
1887     {
1888         if (statement->Postfix())
1889         {
1890             BoundSequenceStatement* sequenceStatement = new BoundSequenceStatement(module, boundStatement->GetSpan(),      std::unique_ptr<BoundStatement>(boundStatement), std::move(statement));
1891             boundStatement = sequenceStatement;
1892         }
1893         else
1894         {
1895             BoundSequenceStatement* sequenceStatement = new BoundSequenceStatement(module, boundStatement->GetSpan(), std::move(statement),      std::unique_ptr<BoundStatement>(boundStatement));
1896             boundStatement = sequenceStatement;
1897         }
1898         if (postfix)
1899         {
1900             boundStatement->SetPostfix();
1901         }
1902     }
1903     statement.reset(boundStatement);
1904 }
